name: 3D shapes
description:
Did you ever wish for a set of 3D shapes you could use in your designs? I gotchu.


This Community template includes 9 different 3D shapes, each in 10 color variations. I added a couple of ideas of how you might use them in the Examples page.


P.S. If you appreciate the work I do, feel free to Buy Me A Coffee or follow my work on Twitter.
